author: Sandee LaMotte, CNN
title: Coronavirus symptoms: 10 key indicators and what to do
description: We are learning more about coronavirus symptoms every day. Here are 10 of the most common symptoms and what to do to keep you and your family safe.
content:
(CNN)Scientists are learning more each day about the mysterious novel coronavirus and the symptoms of Covid-19, the disease it causes.
